ABTMSE
  • Reference
  • Articles

An S4 class object that contains all MSE outputs

Name
The name of the MSE
Date
The date and time the object was created
Author
Who made the object
Notes
Anything noteworthy
PrimarySource
The primary origins of these data
nsim
The number of simulations
npop
number of stocks (e.g. 2, East-West)
nages
number of ages (e.g. 18: 1-17 and 18+)
nyears
number of years of simulation by statistical catch at length
nHyears
number of historical years for stock reduction analysis prior ot statistical catch at length
nsubyears
number of subyears (e.g. 4 quarters)
nareas
number of areas
proyears
number of projection years for closed-loop MSE analysis
nlen
number of length classes
lenbins
vector of length bins that define length classes
interval
how often (number of years) assessments/MPs are implemented (e.g. interval=3 means 2015 assessment, 2016-2017 no assessment, 2018 assessment etc)
nma
number of movement age classes
ma
an array of movement age classes [npop x nage]
mulen
a vector of mean length in each length bin [nage]
Cimp
a vector of imprecision in catch observations (lognormal sd) by simulation [nsim]
Cb
a vector representing the bias in catch observations
Cerr
a matrix of the catch mulitpliers applied to true simulated catch the product of Cimp and Cb [nsim x nyears]
Iimp
currently unused
Ib
currently unused
Ierr
currently unused
nCAAobs
a vector of the number of annual catch-at-age observations by simulation [nsim]
nCALobs
a vector of the number of annual catch-at-length observations by simulation [nsim]
Lcv
currently unused
Mb
a vector of biases in natural mortality rate by simulation [nsim]
Kb
a vector of biases in von-Bert growth parameter K by simulation [nsim]
t0b
a vector of biases in von-Bert growth parameter t0 by simulation [nsim]
Mb
a vector of biases in von-Bert maximum length parameter by simulation [nsim]
LFCb
currently unused
LFSb
currently unused
FMSYb
a vector of biases in fishing mortality rate at MSY by simulation [nsim]
FMSY_Mb
a vector of biases in the ratio of fishing mortality rate at MSY to natural mortality rate by simulation [nsim]
BMSY_B0b
currently unused
ageMb
a vector of biases in the age at 50 per cent maturity [nsim]
Dimp
currently unused
Db
currently unused
Derr
currently unused
Btimp
a vector of imprecision in current biomass observations (lognormal sd) by simulation [nsim]
Btb
a vector representing the bias in current biomass observations
Bterr
a matrix of the mulitpliers applied to true simulated biomass the product of Btimp and Btb [nsim x nyears]
Ftimp
currently unused
Ftb
currently unused
Fterr
currently unused
hb
currently unused
Reccbcv
currently unused
IMSYb
a vector of biases in the index at MSY by simulation [nsim]
IMSYb
a vector of biases in MSY (a reference catch level) by simulation [nsim]
IMSYb
a vector of biases in BMSY (a reference biomass level) by simulation [nsim]
C
a 4D array containing true simulated catches [MP x nsim x nstocks x nyears]
D
a 4D array containing true simulated stock depletion (SSB/SSB0) [MP x nsim x nstocks x nyears]
B_BMSY
a 4D array containing true simulated biomass relative to BMSY [MP x nsim x nstocks x nyears]
F_FMSY
a 4D array containing true simulated fishing mortality rate relative to FMSY [MP x nsim x nstocks x nyears]
B
currently unused
SSB
a 4D array containing true simulated spawning biomass [MP x nsim x nstocks x nyears]
SSB0
a 2D array containing unfished spawnign biomass by simulation and stock [nsim x nstocks]
SSB0proj
a 3D array containing unfished spawning biomass by simulation, stock and projection year [nsim x nstocks x proyears]
TAC
a 4D array containing the TAC recommendations [nsim x MP x stock x proyear]
nMPs
an integer number representing the number of MPs in the MSE
Snames
a character vector naming the stocks [nstocks]
area_defs
a list of area definitions for graphing (lons and lats describing the polygon)
areanams
a character vector of area names
MPs
a list object containing the names of the MPs [nMPs]
